528
00:35:37,244 --> 00:35:38,884
Nobody ever mentioned it again.

529
00:35:40,244 --> 00:35:42,324
Maybe Lei had also forgotten about it.

530
00:35:46,124 --> 00:35:47,244
But I still feel

531
00:35:48,204 --> 00:35:49,364
that I owe him somehow.

532
00:35:54,804 --> 00:35:55,644
I think...

533
00:35:58,764 --> 00:36:00,244
it's time to make it up to him.

534
00:36:03,804 --> 00:36:05,964
Are you talking about Shancai?

535
00:36:11,204 --> 00:36:12,524
I shouldn't torment her anymore.

536
00:36:52,124 --> 00:36:53,124
Shancai, come here.

537
00:36:53,484 --> 00:36:54,804
We have something to tell you.

538
00:37:01,484 --> 00:37:02,324
Dad, Mom.

539
00:37:02,644 --> 00:37:05,044
Sorry. I stayed over
at my friend's place last night.

540
00:37:05,124 --> 00:37:06,484
I wasn't able to tell you about it.

541
00:37:08,084 --> 00:37:08,924
Shancai.

542
00:37:09,204 --> 00:37:10,844
You can't live here anymore.

543
00:37:13,084 --> 00:37:13,924
Why?

544
00:37:15,564 --> 00:37:17,924
Your dad's moving into
a different company housing.

545
00:37:19,044 --> 00:37:20,004
Where?

546
00:37:26,444 --> 00:37:28,684
"Great Earnings Investment
Consulting Corporation."

547
00:37:29,564 --> 00:37:30,844
Dad, really?

548
00:37:31,404 --> 00:37:32,244
That's right.

549
00:37:33,844 --> 00:37:35,844
I had an interview a few days ago.

550
00:37:36,844 --> 00:37:39,524
The boss said that I have a lot
of potential in investment.

551
00:37:40,764 --> 00:37:43,244
Not only does this company
guarantee bonuses,

552
00:37:43,804 --> 00:37:45,084
the salaries are also guaranteed.

553
00:37:45,884 --> 00:37:47,844
I'm going to be rich.

554
00:37:48,684 --> 00:37:50,604
Do you know anything
about investment consulting?

555
00:37:51,204 --> 00:37:53,044
Right? I asked him the same thing.

556
00:37:53,244 --> 00:37:56,324
But he said that the company
has a complete "S" something.

557
00:37:59,364 --> 00:38:00,284
Yes.

558
00:38:02,084 --> 00:38:05,364
Just follow the SOP
and you can get all the benefits

559
00:38:05,644 --> 00:38:06,844
and earn a lot of money.

560
00:38:07,404 --> 00:38:08,724
Is it that simple?

561
00:38:08,804 --> 00:38:09,924
No problem.

562
00:38:10,564 --> 00:38:12,524
I finally found a new career.

563
00:38:14,684 --> 00:38:16,324
If you found a new career,

564
00:38:16,804 --> 00:38:19,164
why do you two look so sad?

565
00:38:19,564 --> 00:38:20,684
Because we have to move.

566
00:38:21,244 --> 00:38:23,044
We lived in this house for over ten years.

567
00:38:23,364 --> 00:38:25,524
Just thinking about it makes me sad.

568
00:38:27,404 --> 00:38:28,364
Furthermore,

569
00:38:28,444 --> 00:38:30,964
my money will be invested in that company,

570
00:38:31,924 --> 00:38:32,804
so...

571
00:38:33,724 --> 00:38:37,164
we'll be living in a place
that is smaller.

572
00:38:37,724 --> 00:38:39,444
Then the kitchen will surely be small.

573
00:38:39,804 --> 00:38:42,404
It'll be inconvenient for me
to cook from now on.

574
00:38:44,724 --> 00:38:46,284
What worries me most is...

575
00:38:49,484 --> 00:38:51,804
How do we pack all this stuff?

576
00:38:53,484 --> 00:38:55,044
Just the souvenirs your mom and I bought

577
00:38:55,124 --> 00:38:57,004
when we traveled together
are already a lot.

578
00:38:57,164 --> 00:38:58,604
-Just throw them away.
-Throw them...

579
00:38:59,404 --> 00:39:00,444
Throw them away?

580
00:39:01,244 --> 00:39:03,044
Those are souvenirs of love.

581
00:39:03,644 --> 00:39:04,484
Throw them...

582
00:39:05,204 --> 00:39:07,204
Shancai, go and pack your things.

583
00:39:07,284 --> 00:39:08,564
We're moving tomorrow.

584
00:39:09,164 --> 00:39:11,244
All right.

585
00:39:15,044 --> 00:39:16,164
What should we do?

586
00:39:30,604 --> 00:39:31,564
Come inside.

587
00:39:32,044 --> 00:39:32,884
We're here.

588
00:39:33,124 --> 00:39:34,244
We're here.

589
00:39:36,244 --> 00:39:37,084
Dear.

590
00:39:37,524 --> 00:39:38,724
This place might not look nice

591
00:39:38,844 --> 00:39:40,084
and it might not be big,

592
00:39:40,284 --> 00:39:41,244
but dear,

593
00:39:41,324 --> 00:39:43,044
with your taste and ideas,

594
00:39:43,284 --> 00:39:46,844
I know you'll turn it into
an intricate and practical place.

595
00:39:47,684 --> 00:39:48,924
Leave it to me.

596
00:39:49,004 --> 00:39:51,364
I'll buy our furniture from
the second-hand store online.

597
00:39:51,444 --> 00:39:52,804
It's economical and practical.

598
00:39:53,164 --> 00:39:56,444
The most important thing is that
we're closer to Shancai's school.

599
00:39:56,844 --> 00:39:59,124
She can sleep half an hour more now.

600
00:39:59,204 --> 00:40:00,164
Am I right?

601
00:40:00,244 --> 00:40:01,844
-Yes.
-Dear, you're so great.

602
00:40:02,444 --> 00:40:03,884
You always think about our family.

603
00:40:04,684 --> 00:40:05,524
Marrying you

604
00:40:05,604 --> 00:40:07,364
was the biggest blessing in my life.

605
00:40:08,004 --> 00:40:09,724
I'll do anything to make our family happy.

606
00:40:10,444 --> 00:40:12,524
Dear, I'll also work hard

607
00:40:12,604 --> 00:40:14,724
for you and our beloved daughter.

608
00:40:15,164 --> 00:40:16,284
I believe in you.

609
00:40:16,884 --> 00:40:19,244
-I'll also work hard.
-Shancai.

610
00:40:19,324 --> 00:40:20,964
You have to study hard.

611
00:40:21,084 --> 00:40:23,684
-You're our family's hope.
-Okay.

612
00:40:23,764 --> 00:40:24,604
-Yes?
-You can do it.

613
00:40:24,684 --> 00:40:26,004
-You can do it.
-I can do it.

614
00:40:32,164 --> 00:40:34,204
Mom, I've already connected the water

615
00:40:34,284 --> 00:40:35,324
-and electricity--
-Hey.

616
00:40:35,404 --> 00:40:36,484
Check them--

617
00:40:39,324 --> 00:40:40,484
Why didn't you say something?

618
00:40:40,564 --> 00:40:42,764
I called out to you.
What were you thinking about?

619
00:40:43,684 --> 00:40:44,524
Nothing.

620
00:40:45,884 --> 00:40:47,524
You left these books at my house.

621
00:40:48,524 --> 00:40:49,764
I completely forgot about them.

622
00:40:50,444 --> 00:40:52,084
Bring your brain with you, will you?

623
00:40:52,164 --> 00:40:53,844
You're always so absent-minded.

624
00:40:55,324 --> 00:40:56,404
All right.

625
00:41:02,124 --> 00:41:03,324
Did you forget something again?

626
00:41:04,044 --> 00:41:05,244
What?

627
00:41:05,324 --> 00:41:07,884
To say thank you.
I brought it to you personally.

628
00:41:09,884 --> 00:41:10,844
Thank you.

629
00:41:16,884 --> 00:41:18,044
<i>It's so strange.</i>

630
00:41:18,284 --> 00:41:20,644
<i>Why is he suddenly acting so normal again?</i>

631
00:41:21,204 --> 00:41:23,444
<i>Shouldn't he be ignoring me?</i>

632
00:41:33,644 --> 00:41:36,084
Frankie Restaurant is looking
for a kitchen assistant.

633
00:41:36,644 --> 00:41:37,484
The hours...

634
00:41:37,684 --> 00:41:39,484
Six to ten at night.

635
00:41:41,164 --> 00:41:42,124
Where is it?

636
00:41:42,204 --> 00:41:43,444
It's near our school.

637
00:41:44,404 --> 00:41:45,244
That's great.

638
00:42:10,124 --> 00:42:11,084
Hi.

639
00:42:11,364 --> 00:42:13,404
I'm here to apply for the kitchen
assistant position.

640
00:42:14,204 --> 00:42:15,524
The kitchen is that way.

641
00:42:16,004 --> 00:42:17,084
Thank you.

642
00:42:35,404 --> 00:42:36,444
Who are you?

643
00:42:37,084 --> 00:42:39,604
Well, I'm here to apply
for the kitchen assistant position.

644
00:42:40,244 --> 00:42:41,084
Kitchen assistant?

645
00:42:42,404 --> 00:42:44,564
We're short on staff right now.
You can start right away.

646
00:42:49,604 --> 00:42:50,844
Peel these potatoes.

647
00:43:19,324 --> 00:43:20,524
Hey, Si.

648
00:43:21,084 --> 00:43:22,684
I never thought you'd recover this fast.

649
00:43:22,764 --> 00:43:24,484
You got over Shancai in just a few days.

650
00:43:25,084 --> 00:43:26,084
Of course.

651
00:43:26,284 --> 00:43:27,364
What was I thinking?

652
00:43:28,444 --> 00:43:30,044
I'm completely over it now.

653
00:43:30,244 --> 00:43:32,084
Who wants such a cheap girl?

654
00:43:32,164 --> 00:43:35,764
If Lei likes her,
I'll tie a bow on her and give her to him.

655
00:43:40,484 --> 00:43:42,284
Speak of the devil.

656
00:43:43,124 --> 00:43:44,244
Who told him to come here?

657
00:43:52,684 --> 00:43:54,244
Why are you suddenly shooting pool?

658
00:43:54,324 --> 00:43:55,164
It's been a while.

659
00:43:56,964 --> 00:43:58,324
It's all because of Si.

660
00:43:58,924 --> 00:44:01,164
I'm not sure what he's thinking.
He told us to come.

661
00:44:02,364 --> 00:44:03,484
-Hey.
-Si.

662
00:44:03,724 --> 00:44:05,564
Didn't you say
you're completely over it now?

663
00:44:09,924 --> 00:44:11,324
Why are you leaving after I arrived?

664
00:44:12,724 --> 00:44:13,964
I'm still mad.

665
00:44:14,564 --> 00:44:15,764
Si, where are you going?

666
00:44:16,004 --> 00:44:17,924
Don't mind him. He's always been that way.

667
00:44:18,004 --> 00:44:19,484
Lei, how did it go last night?

668
00:44:20,204 --> 00:44:21,084
What do you mean?

669
00:44:21,644 --> 00:44:23,204
Don't play dumb. You and Shancai.

670
00:44:24,964 --> 00:44:26,564
You two were alone in the room together.

671
00:44:27,244 --> 00:44:28,284
Did something happen?

672
00:44:33,284 --> 00:44:35,444
Aren't we going to shoot pool? Come on.

673
00:44:36,124 --> 00:44:38,084
Hey, why aren't you answering?

674
00:44:38,164 --> 00:44:39,324
There's nothing to hide.

675
00:44:41,404 --> 00:44:42,844
Shancai is a nice girl.

676
00:44:44,004 --> 00:44:46,604
I admit. I almost fell for her.

677
00:44:48,164 --> 00:44:50,124
But how do I say this?

678
00:44:51,484 --> 00:44:52,964
I won't do anything to her.

679
00:44:55,364 --> 00:44:56,284
Why?

680
00:44:56,884 --> 00:44:59,284
Because I won't betray Si.

681
00:45:00,044 --> 00:45:01,604
He's a good friend that we grew up with.

682
00:45:02,724 --> 00:45:03,564
I see.

683
00:45:04,924 --> 00:45:07,724
If Si learns how to treasure
the person he likes

684
00:45:08,204 --> 00:45:11,244
and realizes that he can't
get everything he wants,

685
00:45:11,404 --> 00:45:14,164
then everything that happened
will have been worth it.

686
00:45:15,764 --> 00:45:16,804
Until then,

687
00:45:17,364 --> 00:45:19,004
I'll keep my distance from Shancai.

688
00:45:20,524 --> 00:45:24,044
He would be so happy to hear that.

689
00:45:25,564 --> 00:45:27,004
I don't plan to tell him.

690
00:45:28,204 --> 00:45:29,124
-Why not?
-Why not?

691
00:45:30,564 --> 00:45:33,284
Because Si did something terrible
to me before.

